OL,3,CHundreds of drivers captured using
OL,4,Cmobile phones by AI cameras
OL,6,FThousands have been caught using their
OL,7,Fmobile phone while driving or not
OL,8,Fwearing their seatbelts by AI cameras
OL,9,Fin just a five week period.
OL,11,FDrivers were seen holding their
OL,12,Fmobiles in front of their face or to
OL,13,Ftheir ear while behind the wheel often
OL,14,Fwith passengers, including children,
OL,15,Fnext to them.
OL,17,FIn several cases the cameras also
OL,18,Ffound drivers, adult and child
OL,19,Fpassengers were not securely fastened
OL,20,Fin their seats, or on some occasions
OL,21,Fnot even wearing seat belts at all.
