OL,3,CHundreds of drivers captured using
OL,4,Cmobile phones by AI cameras
OL,6,FThe potential offenders were each
OL,7,Fcaptured by the state-of-the-art
OL,8,Fcameras in Greater Manchester during a
OL,9,Ftrial which saw the technology rolled
OL,10,Fout across the region's roads.
OL,12,FFootage of passing vehicles recorded
OL,13,Fby the 'Heads Up' cameras then used
OL,14,Fartificial intelligence (AI) to detect
OL,15,Fpotential lawbreaking drivers.
