OL,4,Cmobile phones by AI cameras
OL,6,FAny offences detected as part of the
OL,7,Ftrial can be passed to the police for
OL,8,Fthem to consider further action, but,
OL,9,Fif no offence has been committed, the
OL,10,Fimage is immediately deleted by the
OL,11,Fsoftware and no further action will be
OL,12,Ftaken.
OL,14,FThe trial, carried out by AECOM and
OL,15,FAcusensus on behalf of Safer Roads
OL,16,FGreater Manchester, was held
OL,17,Fthroughout September and October to
OL,18,Fgather data to understand the scale of
OL,19,Fthe issue to inform future education
OL,20,Fcampaigns and enforcement.
