OL,3,CHundreds of drivers captured using
OL,4,Cmobile phones by AI cameras
OL,6,FAs it stands, no offenders have yet
OL,7,Fbeen prosecuted from this trial.
OL,9,FDuring the deployment the Heads Up
OL,10,Fsystem recorded 812 drivers distracted
OL,11,Fby using mobile phones behind the
OL,12,Fwheel, and 2,393 incidents of seat
OL,13,Fbelt non-compliance by drivers or
OL,14,Fpassengers.
