OL,6,FKate Green, Greater Manchester's
OL,7,FDeputy Mayor for Safer and Stronger
OL,8,FCommunities, said: "Distractions such
OL,9,Fas using mobile phones while driving
OL,10,Fand not wearing seat belts are key
OL,11,Ffactors in a number of road traffic
OL,12,Fcollisions on our roads which have
OL,13,Fresulted in people being killed or
OL,14,Fsuffering life-changing injuries.
OL,16,F"This trial was launched so we could
OL,17,Fbetter understand the scale of this
OL,18,Fproblem in Greater Manchester, and the
OL,19,Fimages speak for themselves.
