OL,3,CHundreds of drivers captured using
OL,4,Cmobile phones by AI cameras
OL,6,F"They show drivers who are needlessly
OL,7,Fputting themselves and others `
OL,8,Fincluding young children ` at risk,
OL,9,Fand sadly we know that being
OL,10,Fdistracted for just a second, or not
OL,11,Fwearing a seat belt properly, can have
OL,12,Fdevastating consequences."
OL,14,FShe added: "In Greater Manchester we
OL,15,Fare adopting the Vision Zero ambition
OL,16,Fto end all deaths and life-changing
OL,17,Finjuries, and we know much more needs
OL,18,Fto be done to make our roads safer,
OL,19,Fhealthier and more sustainable for
OL,20,Fpedestrians, cyclists, motorcyclists
OL,21,Fand motorists.
