OL,6,F"I hope these images serve as a wake-
OL,7,Fup call for drivers and passengers on
OL,8,Fthe importance of not driving
OL,9,Fdistracted and seat belt compliance."
OL,11,FDame Sarah Storey, Active Travel
OL,12,FCommissioner for Greater Manchester,
OL,13,Fsaid:"The results of the trial show
OL,14,Fthe horrifying truth behind the number
OL,15,Fof drivers who still don't consider
OL,16,Fhow their behaviour behind the wheel
OL,17,Fof their vehicle can affect
OL,18,Fthemselves, their passengers and other
OL,19,Fpeople using the roads.
