OL,4,Cmobile phones by AI cameras
OL,6,F"Statistics show you are four times
OL,7,Fmore likely to be involved in a
OL,8,Fcollision if you use your phone while
OL,9,Fdriving and twice as likely to die if
OL,10,Fyou don't wear a seatbelt.
OL,12,F"Alongside drink and drug driving and
OL,13,Fspeeding, mobile phone usage and not
OL,14,Fwearing a seat belt make up the Fatal
OL,15,F4, the leading causes of serious
OL,16,Finjury and death on UK roads, which
OL,17,Faffects the lives around 1,000 people
OL,18,Fa year in Greater Manchester.
